  "title": "hierarchicalMenu issue after check a subcategory",
  "body": "I have about 5 categories and each category has another 2 or 3 subcategories. If I check a category the search runs fine but when I check a subcategory the search restart and every category and subcategory appears unchecked.\r\n\r\nThis is my code:\r\n\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n            instantsearch.widgets.hierarchicalMenu({\r\n                container: '#category',\r\n                attributes: ['get_category.lvl1', 'get_category.lvl2', 'get_category.lvl3'],\r\n                sortBy: ['name:asc'],\r\n                templates: {\r\n                    item: function (data) {\r\n\r\n                        checked = \"\"\r\n\r\n                        if (data.isRefined)\r\n                            checked = \"checked\"\r\n\r\n                        return '<label style=\"margin-left: 35px;\" class=\"checkbox filter-checkbox\"><input type=\"checkbox\" value=\"' + data.name + '\" data-toggle=\"checkbox\" ' + checked + '> ' + data.name + '</label>'\r\n                    }\r\n                },\r\n                cssClasses: {\r\n                    body: 'filterCheckbox'\r\n                }\r\n            })\r\n        );",
